<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="c26Jan1938"><font color="red">26 January 1938</font> <i>NLVP</i> (from Ben Huebsch to Paul L&eacute;on): July 4th &hellip; would be bad for the new book &hellip; I think we ought to have four or five months after receipt of definitive manuscript in which to do the right thing by the book. </div>
